description.excerpt: The project includes has the original implementations for the following network embedding techniques.
Please refer to the original papers:

This project holds the implementations done by DeepWalk, node2vec and struc2vec network embedding techniques. Through them the idea would be to propose a new network embedding system. A survey has been done, but more information can be found in the project's website.
